OL,7,FBaroness Merron, who is currently
OL,8,Frenewing the Women's Health Strategy,
OL,9,Fsaid the meeting came "at the perfect
OL,10,Ftime" and insisted it would help shape
OL,11,Fimprovements in care.
OL,13,FShe said she was "very moved" by the
OL,14,Faccounts from campaigners affected by
OL,15,Fthe condition.
OL,17,F"I'm very grateful that the women I
OL,18,Fmet were so honest and open about
OL,19,Ftheir experiences," she said.
