OL,7,FCampaigners told the Baroness that
OL,8,Fdespite national guidance, many women
OL,9,Fare repeatedly turned away from care,
OL,10,Fdenied appropriate anti-sickness
OL,11,Fmedication and accused of exaggerating
OL,12,Ftheir symptoms.
OL,14,FHarry Potter actor Afshan Azad was
OL,15,Famong those who attended the meeting.
OL,16,FShe described the lack of appropriate
OL,17,Fsupport for those with hyperemesis as
OL,18,F"a major women's health issue" and
OL,19,Fsaid it consumed her entire life.
