OL,7,F"The relentless vomiting, dehydration,
OL,8,Fsevere weight loss, and the fear that
OL,9,Fdominated every single hour of every
OL,10,Fsingle day," she said. "It isn't just
OL,11,Fmorning sickness. It's a debilitating
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,F"What shocked me even more was how
OL,15,Funprepared the system was to support
OL,16,Fme. I was passed from one professional
OL,17,Fto another, told this is normal, go
OL,18,Fhome.
