OL,7,F"I was made to feel I was exaggerating
OL,8,F(...) and that feeling of being
OL,9,Fdismissed when you're at your lowest
OL,10,Fpoint can be just as traumatic."
OL,12,FBaroness Merron acknowledged that
OL,13,Fwomen's concerns were too often
OL,14,Fdismissed. "The biggest message in all
OL,15,Fof this is women are not being heard,"
OL,16,Fshe said. "They are not being heard,
OL,17,Fand that is totally unacceptable."
