OL,7,FContent creator and podcast host, Em
OL,8,FClarkson host who documented her
OL,9,Fexperience of hyperemesis on social
OL,10,Fmedia, was visibly emotional during
OL,11,Fthe discussion.
OL,13,FShe said afterwards: "I'm frustrated
OL,14,Fat myself for crying because I fear it
OL,15,Fundermines my point. But it probably
OL,16,Fmakes my point more succinctly than
OL,17,Fany words I can say."
OL,19,F"HG was the single most traumatising
OL,20,Fthing I have been through. I have not
