OL,7,FCampaigners raised the well-documented
OL,8,Fdifficulty many women face in
OL,9,Faccessing Xonvea, the only medication
OL,10,Fin the UK licensed specifically for
OL,11,Fpregnancy sickness. They told Merron
OL,12,Fthe patchwork of prescribing practices
OL,13,Fmeans some patients are left without
OL,14,Feffective treatment.
OL,16,FIn response, Merron said she would
OL,17,Fexamine prescribing variation across
OL,18,Fthe country and set clearer
OL,19,Fexpectations for clinicians.
