OL,7,FThe meeting fell three years to the
OL,8,Fday that Jess Cronshaw took her own
OL,9,Flife while suffering from HG. At the
OL,10,Finquest into her death, the coroner
OL,11,Fconcluded that failings in Jess' care
OL,12,Fcontributed to the deterioration in
OL,13,Fher mental health.
OL,15,FHer Mum, Susan Cronshaw previously
OL,16,Ftold ITV News she fears other women
OL,17,Fwill die if care isn't improved across
OL,18,Fthe UK.
