OL,7,FAsked whether hyperemesis would be
OL,8,Fformally included in the government's
OL,9,Fnew maternal safety review, Baroness
OL,10,FMerron said the process was
OL,11,Findependent but confirmed the review
OL,12,Fteam had already chosen to engage with
OL,13,Fcampaigners.
OL,15,F"It is an independent review, so they
OL,16,Fwill make the decision," she said.
OL,17,F"But I do know they've already decided
OL,18,Fthey will be talking with the
OL,19,Fcampaigners about hyperemesis."
