OL,7,FCharlotte urged the Minister to review
OL,8,Fcurrent patient pathways. She
OL,9,Fhighlighted that some are referred by
OL,10,FGPs to early pregnancy units, which
OL,11,Fare primarily set up for viability
OL,12,Fscans, or they end up in A&E where
OL,13,Fthere's a lack of expertise in HG.
