OL,7,F"If I were to ask anything today ...
OL,8,Fit would be to review the current
OL,9,Fpathways ... starting with primary
OL,10,Fcare," she said. Howden stressed that,
OL,11,Fgiven NHS resource constraints, she
OL,12,Fwas not calling for an entirely new
OL,13,Fsystem ` but for better use of
OL,14,Fexisting maternity infrastructure.
OL,15,F"Where can these women go within
OL,16,Fmaternity that would be suitable? They
OL,17,Fneed to be managed and supported by
OL,18,Fmidwives and obstetricians who have
OL,19,Fthe proper training."
