OL,3,CPregnancy sickness: Government vows to
OL,4,Cact after hearing 'deeply tragic'
OL,5,Cstories
OL,7,FCharlotte Howden (PSS) expressed
OL,8,Fcautious optimism, "I don't want to
OL,9,Fjinx things, but it did feel like it
OL,10,Fwas different. We've been here before.
OL,11,FHyperemesis was named on the previous
OL,12,Fwomen's health strategy, and I do
OL,13,Fbelieve the Minister was talking about
OL,14,Freinvigorating that strategy."
OL,16,F"I'm always sceptical because of the
OL,17,Ffact we have been doing this for over
OL,18,F20 years. But I'm very hopeful that
OL,19,Fthis could be a positive step forward
OL,20,Ffor the future of sufferers in the UK."
