OL,7,FEm Clarkson reflected on the
OL,8,Fsignificance of the meeting: "I'm
OL,9,Freally hopeful. I'm really optimistic."
OL,11,F"I think the thing that I always
OL,12,Fcraved and wanted when I was suffering
OL,13,Fand the thing that I still want very
OL,14,Fbadly now is for there to be hope for
OL,15,Fother women going through it. The fact
OL,16,Fthat it happened at all, that we got
OL,17,Fthe opportunity that anything good
OL,18,Fmight come of this, does feel very
OL,19,Fgood to me."
